parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of Takata airbag recall parts can lead to delayed or incomplete repairs, leaving drivers at risk of airbag failure in the event of an accident, which can cause serious injury or death.
symptoms: None reported
as the issue is related to the unavailability of parts for recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident can cause serious injury or death.
symptoms: The check airbag warning light illuminates on the instrument control panel
but the airbags fail to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the door to become stuck, making it difficult or impossible to open or close, which can lead to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The door lock actuator constantly tries to lock the doors
the door will not open when the door handle is touched
the driver-side door lock control will not lock or unlock the front passenger door.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery and electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The vehicle will not start
the battery drains quickly
the vehicle stalls without warning
electrical warning lights come on
the air conditioning system fails
the cooling system warning light comes on
the temperature gauge fluctuates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent stalling and sudden acceleration can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls without warning
the vehicle lurches forward when lifting foot off brake
sudden acceleration occurs in heavy traffic.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering wheel lock can cause the vehicle to become stuck, making it difficult or impossible to move, which can lead to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The steering wheel locks with the wheels in any position
the driver has to relieve the pressure on the lock before the ignition switch will turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inadequate headlight illumination can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: Headlights do not illuminate the road far enough ahead
making it difficult to see obstacles or navigate through turns
creating hazardous driving conditions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Misaligned headlights can cause reduced visibility, glare, and discomfort for oncoming traffic, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Projector headlights are aimed too low
making it difficult to see in normal city conditions
especially on backroads.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Intermittent headlight failure can cause sudden loss of visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: Headlights randomly quit working
sometimes on one side and then on both sides
requiring the headlight switch to be turned off and back on to restore functionality.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: PAX Tire System Failure and Maintenance Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PAX tire system can lead to tire blowouts, loss of control, and accidents, which can result in injuries or fatalities. The lack of adequate repair facilities, specialized training, and equipment can cause delays and inconvenience to consumers, potentially leading to further safety risks.
symptoms: Tire blowouts
tire deflation
bubbles on the tire
cracked rims
difficulty finding repair facilities
long wait times for repairs
and high replacement costs.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Insufficient Disclosure of PAX Tire System Limitations
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of transparency about the PAX tire system's limitations, such as its limited lifespan and high maintenance costs, can lead to consumer dissatisfaction, financial losses, and potential safety risks.
symptoms: Unawareness of the PAX tire system's limitations
unexpected high replacement costs
and feeling deceived by the manufacturer.
